  <prompt>
    Finalize subpath exports map in `@spaarke/daily-briefing-components/package.json` per FR-10. Exports: `./components`, `./widgets`, `./hooks`, `./services`, `./types`. Verify all five subpaths resolve from a consumer import. Also export a default barrel from `./` for legacy single-import consumers.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in `package.json` exports map and Pattern D subpath conventions.</role>

  <goal>Subpath exports map matches Calendar + Smart Todo precedent; all five subpaths resolve from a test consumer.</goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per FR-10: subpath contract per `@spaarke/events-components` precedent. Consumers (DailyBriefing solution, LegalWorkspace shim, SpaarkeAi shim) import from named subpaths.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/client/shared/Spaarke.DailyBriefing.Components/package.json</file>
      <file>src/client/shared/Spaarke.Events.Components/package.json</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Subpath exports per Pattern D convention.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Five subpaths required (FR-10); a default barrel export from `./` is allowed for ergonomics.</constraint>
  </constraints>

